{"tid":779024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特區政府對外國記者會邀請陳浩天演講深表遺憾","createTime":"2018-08-14T06:37:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T07:23:41.000Z","uid":4783,"like":9,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"40304f99b36d14f330d9dcfef637755e9b86e87e","tid":779024,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T06:37:26.000Z","msg":"14.08.2018 14:34<br />\n民族黨召集人陳浩天在外國記者會演講，特區政府發聲明，表示對香港外國記者會，邀請鼓吹港獨的講者在午餐會上演講深表遺憾，指政府一直支持香港外國記者會的工作，但外國記者會這次的做法，是完全漠視香港維護國家主權的憲制責任，政府完全不能接受。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人強調，任何人公開宣揚及鼓吹 「港獨」是完全不恰當亦不能接受。鼓吹 「港獨」 不但公然違反《基本法》，更直接損害國家主權、國家安全及領土完整，有違全面貫徹落實 「 一國兩制 」，破壞香港特別行政區在《基本法》列明的憲制與法律基礎。特區政府十分重視新聞自由和言論自由，這些自由是受到《基本法》保障，但並非絕對，必須依法行使。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1024403&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1024403%26csid%3D261_341&d=ZKH8qiq0938nELvGat%2FllJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=478b7a60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1024403&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"304aed0a52149b7b7c9b88e4de84aa81e8220627","tid":779024,"uid":155818,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T06:38:00.000Z","msg":"口交部"},{"pid":"e4839f00d3ab9d353129b206078582ad07703184","tid":779024,"uid":11001,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T06:39:02.000Z","msg":"遺憾咪遺憾囉，佢有邊日唔遺憾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/